      • addJobRegistryForClass

        public JobRegistry addJobRegistryForClass​(DiscoveryApplication application,
                                          java.lang.String userId,
                                          java.lang.String requestCode,
                                          java.lang.String node,
                                          java.lang.String tripleStore,
                                          java.lang.String className,
                                          boolean doSync,
                                          java.lang.String webHook,
                                          boolean propagueInKafka,
                                          boolean searchLinks,
                                          boolean applyDelta)
        Handle a new Job for search similitudes by class
        Parameters:
        application - DiscoveryApplication The discovery application to which the job belongs
        userId - String. The userId for handle the response
        requestCode - String. The requestCode for handle the response
        node - String. The node where we want search similitudes
        tripleStore - String. The triple store where we want search similitudes
        className - String. The class name where we want search similitudes
        doSync - boolean. Do or not the operation in synchronous mode
        webHook - String. Web Hook where the call back will be done
        propagueInKafka - boolean. Do or not the response propagation in kafka
        searchLinks - boolean. Do or not the search of similarities in other nodes
        applyDelta - boolean. Do or not the search only with deltas since the last modification
        Returns:
        JobRegistry with the results id is synchronous, else Job registry with the request id for get the response when the Job will be finished
        See Also:
        DiscoveryApplication, JobRegistry

        Handle a new Job for search similitudes by class in the LOD cloud
        Parameters:
        application - DiscoveryApplication The discovery application to which the job belongs
        userId - String. The userId for handle the response
        requestCode - String. The requestCode for handle the response
        node - String. The node where we want search similitudes
        tripleStore - String. The triple store where we want search similitudes
        className - String. The class name where we want search similitudes
        doSync - boolean. Do or not the operation in synchronous mode
        webHook - String. Web Hook where the call back will be done
        propagueInKafka - boolean. Do or not the response propagation in kafka
        applyDelta - boolean. Do or not the search only with deltas since the last modification
        applyDelta - String. The name of the dataset where will be done the search
        Returns:
        JobRegistry with the results id is synchronous, else Job registry with the request id for get the response when the Job will be finished

        DiscoveryApplication, JobRegistry
